---
// ICP Segment Cards - showing the 5 buyer archetypes with trigger language
---

<section class="icp-section section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="icp-header">
      <h2>Sound Familiar?</h2>
      <p class="icp-intro">
        These are the conversations we have every week. If one hits close to home, we should talk.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="icp-grid">
      <!-- CRO -->
      <div class="icp-card">
        <div class="icp-role">CRO</div>
        <p class="icp-trigger">
          "Sales is using ChatGPT. Marketing has different AI tools. CS has their own. I have no idea what's being said to customers."
        </p>
        <p class="icp-outcome">
          Unified AI layer. Shared context. Controlled outputs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- VP Sales -->
      <div class="icp-card">
        <div class="icp-role">VP Sales</div>
        <p class="icp-trigger">
          "Every new operator starts from zero. Our best closer's playbook isn't captured anywhere the team can use."
        </p>
        <p class="icp-outcome">
          A system that learns from every deal. Best practices compound.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- CFO -->
      <div class="icp-card">
        <div class="icp-role">CFO</div>
        <p class="icp-trigger">
          "We're paying for 7 tools that don't talk to each other. Now everyone wants AI budget I can't measure."
        </p>
        <p class="icp-outcome">
          Infrastructure that consolidates, not fragments. Measurable ROI.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- RevOps Director -->
      <div class="icp-card">
        <div class="icp-role">RevOps Director</div>
        <p class="icp-trigger">
          "I'm drowning in tickets. No bandwidth to re-architect for AI or build unified data layers."
        </p>
        <p class="icp-outcome">
          Infrastructure partners, not consultants. We deploy so you strategize.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- PE Operating Partner -->
      <div class="icp-card">
        <div class="icp-role">PE Operating Partner</div>
        <p class="icp-trigger">
          "Portfolio company has a CRM mess. Board wants unified revenue stack in 90 days."
        </p>
        <p class="icp-outcome">
          We start in 2 weeks, bring our own AI layer, and deliver.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .icp-section {
    background-color: var(--section-dark-bg);
  }

  .icp-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .icp-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .icp-intro {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .icp-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .icp-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1100px) {
    .icp-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }

    /* Make last two cards center on larger screens */
    .icp-card:nth-child(4) {
      grid-column: 1 / 2;
    }

    .icp-card:nth-child(5) {
      grid-column: 2 / 3;
    }
  }

  .icp-card {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    border: 2px solid var(--border-subtle);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .icp-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--sky-blue, var(--roi-green));
  }

  .icp-role {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--sky-blue, var(--roi-green));
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .icp-trigger {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .icp-trigger::before {
    content: '"';
  }

  .icp-trigger::after {
    content: '"';
  }

  .icp-outcome {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
